high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead, and then head right to the stove.
Take the pot off the front left burner.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot on the bottom shelf of the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the pot on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a stove top.

high_descs: Turn right and head across the room, at the coffee maker turn right and walk to the stove
Pick up the pot that is sitting on the right hand burner closest to you
Turn around and cross the room to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the pot on the bottom shelf to the left of the lettuce then close the door.  Open the fridge and pick up the pot that is on the bottom shelf
Turn around and walk to the stove
Place the pot on the right back burner
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a stove

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the large metal pot off of the front left burner of the stove.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the large metal pot inside on the bottom shelf and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge door remove the large metal pot and close the fridge door.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the stove.
Put the chilled large metal pot on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled large metal pot on the back left burner of the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the coffee maker, and then turn right towards the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot next to the lettuce, close the fridge and wait for it to cool take the pot out of the fridge.
Turn around and walk towards the stove.
Place the pot behind the pan on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the toaster then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pot from the bottom left burner.
Turn around and walk to the fridge so you are in front of it facing it.
Chill the pot on the bottom shelf by the lettuce before taking it back out again closing the refrigerator door.
Turn around and walk to the stove so you are in front of it facing it again.
Place the pot on the top right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on top of the stove.

high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead, and then hang right to the stove.
Pick up the pot.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot on the bottom shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and then pick up the pot again.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pot on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on a stove.
